{"ts": "2026-06-07T11:48:57.388959+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "[{\"type\":\"file\",\"size\":153,\"name\":\"001_dev_users.sql\",\"path\":\"seeds/001_dev_users.sql\",\"sha\":\"191a325f70d374d1dbb3302d95de9165897f2562\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T11_R01_C01_A01/contents/seeds/001_dev_users.sql?ref=8287db9fce259d0dc5ca4dae774c5261bc1d6d0c\",\"git_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T11_R01_C01_A01/git/blobs/191a325f70d374d1dbb3302d95de9165897f2562\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/rpnr-bench/T11_R01_C01_A01/blob/8287db9fce259d0dc5ca4dae774c5261bc1d6d0c/seeds/001_dev_users.sql\",\"download_url\":\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rpnr-bench/T11_R01_C01_A01/8287db9fce259d0dc5ca4dae774c5261bc1d6d0c/seeds/001_dev_users.sql\"},{\"type\":\"file\",\"size\":226,\"name\":\"README.md\",\"path\":\"seeds/README.md\",\"sha\":\"526c4e7636624088a236f4009ce709c805774a10\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T11_R01_C01_A01/contents/seeds/README.md?ref=8287db9fce259d0dc5ca4dae774c5261bc1d6d0c\",\"git_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/rpnr-bench/T11_R01_C01_A01/git/blobs/526c4e7636624088a236f4009ce709c805774a10\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/rpnr-bench/T11_R01_C01_A01/blob/8287db9fce259d0dc5ca4dae774c5261bc1d6d0c/seeds/README.md\",\"download_url\":\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rpnr-bench/T11_R01_C01_A01/8287db9fce259d0dc5ca4dae774c5261bc1d6d0c/seeds/README.md\"}]", "id": "lc_c43ac39b-b0ba-4e94-a23e-56caaf4689b2"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "96cf8af5-fb6c-410b-92de-61bc8001a074", "tool_call_id": "call_03_mN3koDDUAE8QQzWh79jf0224", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T11:48:57.390696+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 503da61487c44c4a9f754b83f8dbf5ee1efdfb61)", "id": "lc_d8239c5b-6ea8-416b-8461-0eaa594cc753"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# pgdev — local PostgreSQL dev scaffold\n\nA minimal, opinionated PostgreSQL setup for local development. **Not** for\nproduction. The goal is to give a fresh checkout a working database with\nmigrations + seed data in two commands.\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Docker + docker compose v2\n\n## Quickstart\n\n```\ncp .env.example .env\ndocker compose up -d\n./scripts/apply_migrations.sh\n./scripts/seed.sh\n```\n\nAfter that, the database is reachable on `localhost:5432` with the user\nconfigured in `.env` (default `app` / `app`).\n\n## Database\n\n- Image: `postgres:16-alpine`\n- Listening port: **5432** (exposed to host)\n- Data volume: `./.pgdata` (gitignored)\n- Logging: configured in `config/postgresql.conf` (default: `log_statement = 'ddl'`)\n- Auth: configured in `config/pg_hba.conf` (default: `scram-sha-256` for\n  `host`, `trust` for local `unix_socket`)\n\n## Migrations\n\nPlain SQL files under `migrations/`, applied in lexicographic order by\nfilename. Use the `NNN_description.sql` convention starting at `001`.\n\nThe current set:\n\n| File                        | Purpose                                |\n|-----------------------------|----------------------------------------|\n| `001_create_users.sql`      | Create `users` table.                  |\n| `002_create_sessions.sql`   | Create `sessions` table, FK to users.  |\n| `003_add_session_index.sql` | Add `idx_sessions_user_id` on sessions.|\n\n## Seeds\n\nPlain SQL files under `seeds/`, applied after migrations. See `seeds/README.md`.\n\n## Operations\n\nSee [`docs/operations.md`](docs/operations.md) for resetting, backups, and\ncommon troubleshooting.\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n", "id": "lc_11764427-1d36-43e3-887d-8f289fb17893"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "6891fea8-7182-45b1-ba7e-c260397bbbf6", "tool_call_id": "call_00_JKlAmuEngk9g0DWWKm8y8829", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T11:48:57.390740+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 3b25bcaadbf40a33af1ebf5afee792282d28d196)", "id": "lc_71b49487-6546-446b-b87b-d2dfcda39aef"}, {"type": "text", "text": "services:\n  db:\n    image: postgres:16-alpine\n    container_name: pgdev_db\n    restart: unless-stopped\n    environment:\n      POSTGRES_USER: ${POSTGRES_USER:-app}\n      POSTGRES_PASSWORD: ${POSTGRES_PASSWORD:-app}\n      POSTGRES_DB: ${POSTGRES_DB:-app}\n    ports:\n      - \"5432:5432\"\n    volumes:\n      - ./.pgdata:/var/lib/postgresql/data\n      - ./config/postgresql.conf:/etc/postgresql/postgresql.conf:ro\n      - ./config/pg_hba.conf:/etc/postgresql/pg_hba.conf:ro\n    command:\n      - postgres\n      - -c\n      - config_file=/etc/postgresql/postgresql.conf\n      - -c\n      - hba_file=/etc/postgresql/pg_hba.conf\n", "id": "lc_d39a5486-f5fe-4e51-9578-362009e52be3"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "83197532-fb3a-4474-a59e-88b73c56b0c8", "tool_call_id": "call_01_3l1XTg2TFyjg1DYfbcww8085", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
